            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                [Cornelia<del rend="erasure">e Saloni</del>]<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">nae</supplied> san<supplied reason="lost">c</supplied>tissimae <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>ustae</ex></expan> matri castro<lb break="no" n="4"/>rum coniugi <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>omini</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>ostri</ex></expan> <del rend="erasure">G<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>l</del><lb break="no" n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">lieni In</supplied>victi <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usti</ex></expan> ac <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">super omn</supplied>es retro <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">principes</supplied> fortissimi <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">senatus c</supplied><expan><abbr>ol</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> Falis<lb break="no" n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">corum de</supplied>votus <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">numini</supplied> maiesta<lb break="no" n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">tique eiu</supplied>s curan<lb break="no" n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">te Tyrio</supplied> Septi<lb break="no" n="13"/><supplied reason="lost">mio Azi</supplied>zo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>erfectissimo</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/><supplied reason="lost">curator</supplied>e ope<lb break="no" n="15"/>rum <supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>t rei <expan><abbr>publ</abbr><ex>icae</ex></expan> <lb n="16"/><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>orum
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Ursprüngliche Größe der Basis nach Di Stefano Manzella: circa 142-150 x 57-59 cm. Heute ist nur noch der rechte Teil erhalten; Text des linken Teils teilweise noch handschriftlich überliefert. Horster: Z. 1 u. 4: Eradierungen nicht angegeben; Z. 10/11: maiestat/[ique eiu]s; Z. 15: et.</p>
            </div>
